{%- if kotlin_convention %}
- Kotlin and the Java {{ java_version }} toolchain are configured by the
  `kotlin-conventions` plugin in `buildSrc/`.
{%- else %}
- Kotlin and the Java {{ java_version }} toolchain are configured inline in
